Package: polyprof
Type: Package
Title: Easier analysis of polysome profiles (usually)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("José Francisco", "Martínez Hernández", , "jfmh@sund.ku.dk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3457-2088"))
Maintainer: <jfmh@sund.ku.dk>
Description: Some functions which just make it easier to format polysome profiles for their visulization, and some which can aid in their analysis. Some functions assume that the profiles have `Position (mm)` and `Absorbance` columns.
License: use_mit_license()
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
